# Copy to `.env.local` and adjust. Vite bakes `VITE_*` at dev/build time.

# Optional — only for `yarn dev` when you are not loading the SPA through Spring
# (the served HTML sets `globalThis.__FLAGSMITH_ENVIRONMENT_KEY__` from
# `BIBLIVRE_FLAGSMITH_ENVIRONMENT_KEY` instead).
# Create a boolean feature named `search_excel_export` in the same Flagsmith project.
# VITE_FLAGSMITH_ENVIRONMENT_KEY=

# JVM / Docker: set BIBLIVRE_FLAGSMITH_ENVIRONMENT_KEY to the Flagsmith client-side
# environment key so the SPA HTML can inject it at runtime.

# Backend (env flags provider): set FLAG_SEARCH_EXCEL_EXPORT=true or the export API returns no permission.
